title: TNF Recap; Week 4 Preview
itunes:title: TNF Recap; Week 4 Preview
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, & Gregg Rosenthal recap all the latest news and preview all the upcoming match-ups for week 4. The heroes also recap the Green Bay Packers beat down on the Chicago Bears during Thursday Night Football. Will there be another "lock off" this week?
